article.description: — Greg Parham scored 22 points and VMI topped Longwood 84-71 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Parham scores 22 to lead VMI over Longwood 84-71
article.linkText: Parham scores 22 to lead VMI over Longwood 84-71
article.story: LEXINGTON, Va. -- — Greg Parham scored 22 points and VMI topped Longwood 84-71 on Tuesday. Sean Conway added a career-high 19 points for the Keydets (2-1). Jake Stephens added 13 points. Kamdyn Curfman had 11 points. Myles Lewis had 6 points and 11 rebounds. Juan Munoz had 18 points for the Lancers (0-2). Justin Hill added 15 points and six assists. Christian Wilson had 11 points and seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
